    <title>前端单元测试和持续集成</title>
    <link href="https://liuyib.github.io/2019/06/04/front-end-unit-test-and-ci/"/>
    <id>https://liuyib.github.io/2019/06/04/front-end-unit-test-and-ci/</id>
    <published>2019-06-04T14:54:49.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-02T08:00:28.015Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;前端的单元测试包括但不限于：单元功能测试、UI 测试、兼容性测试等等。一个测试体系大体包括四部分：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;测试运行器（e.g. &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/karma-runner/karma&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Karma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;测试框架（e.g. &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/mochajs/mocha&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Mocha&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/facebook/jest&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Jest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/jasmine/jasmine&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Jasmine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Qunit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;断言库（e.g. &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/shouldjs/should.js&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Should&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/chaijs/chai&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Chai&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;测试覆盖率（e.g. &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;exturl__link&quot;   href=&quot;https://github.com/gotwarlost/istanbul&quot;  target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Istanbul&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;exturl__icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fas fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
